hip (slant edge) angle omega of right pyramid with regular base
Kantenwinkel an den Seiten einer Pyramide mit regelmäßiger Grundfläche

first impression -> images/PyramideSkizzeOpenGL.pdf
erster Überblick -> images/PyramideSkizzeOpenGL.pdf

If you like to calculate without graphic output
start ./polygon-pyramid-hip-angle.rb on commandline

./polygon-pyramid-hip-angle.rb 3 10 20
returns the values for a pyramid with 3 edges on base, an edge-length of 10 and a height of 20

If you like to get some grafics too, try
./pyramid4.rb to get some data about a regular square pyramid or
./pget.rb to play with a regular pyramid from 3 to 99 base edges.


Norbert Reschke 1988...

